commit.message: Fixed simu-shot glitch, updated bundle info

Thrusters aligned properly, leaderboard scores now load properly

A wild "Khela Chele" has appeared!
Achievements partially implemented, coming soon placeholder gone
High and low score leaderboards added
Fixed launch screen, added x3 app icons
Ships change color based on your save, fixed minor sound bugs
Shortened laser and explosion sound effects
Game doesn't automatically go idle & stays paused even when woken
Power ups fall slower and occur more frequently, invincibility animation changed
Music lag alleviated, power ups can't be shot
Added timer for powerups and made them less common
Power ups fall and can interact with player
Improved health bar & added power up assets
